title: Stock market today: Dow and S&P 500 rise, Nasdaq pares losses as key ADP jobs data shows weakness
description: Doubts over AI demand put pressure on tech and a surprise fall in private-sector employment revealed cracks in the job market.
content:
The Dow led diverging US stocks on Wednesday as doubts over AI demand put pressure on tech, and a surprise fall in private-sector employment revealed cracks in the job market.
